					<description><![CDATA[James, I support 110% of every word in this post. 

It&#039;s the most comprehensive and perfect (nothing to take off) post on habits that worth giving everyone who wants to change their lives.

You know what? This is the exact process I used to:

- Read 150 books last year.
- Meditate for 120 days already.
- Take cold showers everytime. 
- Eating my frog habit (1 week in. :) Feeling good.)
- Sustain my sleep pattern (in the process).

I would like to say that success rate for this process is ~90%-100% (vs 80-90% fail rate for average), so basically it&#039;s the huge difference. The key is patience.

Thank you very much for your writing. It definitely influenced and changed my life. 

Have a great day and give MORE strategic content. :)

David.]]></description>
