					<description><![CDATA[Hi James

I really like your problem no 5. Small changes do add up if you give them a chance.

I am working on a big writing project this year and have decided to tackle it by writing for 20 minutes 5 days a week. I might not achieve many words in that time but cumulatively, the word count is growing and I am already seeing the results.

I would encourage anyone to give small changes a try

Jo]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hi James</p>
<p>I really like your problem no 5. Small changes do add up if you give them a chance.</p>
<p>I am working on a big writing project this year and have decided to tackle it by writing for 20 minutes 5 days a week. I might not achieve many words in that time but cumulatively, the word count is growing and I am already seeing the results.</p>
<p>I would encourage anyone to give small changes a try</p>
<p>Jo</p>
