					<description><![CDATA[Great as always James! I can attest to the fact that a Keystone habit can make all the difference. About a year ago I started &quot;My Morning Blastoff.&quot; It&#039;s pretty much a series of events that get me in the zone for whatever the day holds. It has been so effective my accountability partner can notice without me saying, whether or not I did it for the day. It&#039;s also been a great way for me to build new habits because I just attach them to the Morning Blastoff. Thanks for all the tips &#038; hope all is well.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Great as always James! I can attest to the fact that a Keystone habit can make all the difference. About a year ago I started &#8220;My Morning Blastoff.&#8221; It&#8217;s pretty much a series of events that get me in the zone for whatever the day holds. It has been so effective my accountability partner can notice without me saying, whether or not I did it for the day. It&#8217;s also been a great way for me to build new habits because I just attach them to the Morning Blastoff. Thanks for all the tips &amp; hope all is well.</p>
