<p>I&#8217;ve made every mistake on this list, multiple times. But each time I try and fail, I get closer to succeeding. Focussing on only one area or habit at a time has to be my biggest problem, as with so many life areas that need improvement, I tend to try and work on multiple things at once. B.J.&#8217;s Tiny Habit program may be just what I need to help me succeed.</p>
