			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>A perfect post to start the New Year!  I think your fourth problem resonates with me the most.  Our environment can be extremely important.  In my case, I&#8217;m surrounded by certain people that are not encouraging of new positive work habits so I am looking to make some changes.  </p>
<p>Moreover, in order to become more focused (huge resolution of mine), I must limit the number of distractions during work hours.  This means cell phone in another room, Self-Control app installed on Macbook, and closing the office door when doing most important tasks.</p>
